<p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241221/1734781089267000435.png" title="1734781089267000435.png" alt="屏幕截图 2024-12-21 193844.png" width="774" height="571" style="width: 774px; height: 571px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">为了深化入党积极分子对党的认知，夯实思想根基，进一步提升政治素养与理论水平，2024年12月18日18时，经济管理学院第32期入党积极分子学班于A10-311开展了以“学习党史：党的理论和历史光辉历程”为主题的集体学习。本次学习由班长张佳探领学。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241221/1734781210830001973.jpg" title="1734781210830001973.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241221194046.jpg" width="774" height="556" style="width: 774px; height: 556px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">首先，张佳探从党的指导思想具体内容、党的百年光辉奋斗历程、遵义会议作为重要转折点的重要意义三方面带领学班进行了集体学习。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">中国共产党的成立是中国历史上开天辟地的大事变，为中国革命指明了方向，为中国的独立和人民的解放奠定了基础。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241221/1734781283427022728.jpg" title="1734781283427022728.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241221194053.jpg" width="802" height="485" style="width: 802px; height: 485px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">接着，张佳探组织全体学班成员观看党史视频。在这个过程中，大家仿佛置身于历史的长河之中，亲眼见证了党从诞生到壮大，从艰难曲折到走向辉煌的壮丽篇章。</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">心得分享<br/></span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20241221/1734781380928011429.jpg" title="1734781380928011429.jpg" alt="微信图片_20241221194115.jpg" width="819" height="550" style="width: 819px; height: 550px;"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">通过了解党的历史，我更加深入地理解了党的初心和使命，在学习遵义会议等历史事件时，我深刻感受到了党在革命时期所经历的艰难曲折和党的英明决策。同时，我更加明白了只有坚持党的领导，才能推动中国革命和建设事业不断向前发展。我还认识到了自己在入党道路上存在很多不足和需要努力的地方。我将继续加强学习，不断提高自己的政治觉悟和思想认识，积极向党组织靠拢。</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px; text-indent: 2em;">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; --B230504 余倩兰</span></p><p style="text-align: center; text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">结语</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;;">通过本次集体学习，我们深刻地认识到了党的伟大和正确，也更加坚定了自己为党的事业奋斗终身的信念。作为入党积极分子，我们肩负着重要的责任和使命，必须在实践熔炉里检验真知，以实际行动丈量党史精神厚度，初心不改，砥砺前行。</span></p>